                                  Exhibit Central

     Multimedia 
      Taking Black Holes for a Spin
      What's the different between black holes that spin and those that
    don't? Quite a lot it turns out. Our latest video feature illustrates
    the differences, and describes the evidence used to detect a rotating
    black hole.
      What a Blast
      An AVI/QuickTime video on a mysterious "bursting pulsar."
